DOCKER
Docker networking:
the base how docker manage those is depande on some lunix core features ``here we talk about lunix the kernal``
    Network Namespaces:
        is base feature that provid in isolation between the containers in the networking context
    Virtual Ethernet Devices (veth pairs):
        is basedly used to connect tow isolated containers, usually attached to a virtual bridge.
    iptables:
        iptables rules (a firewall utility) to manage port to manage te port mapping and NAT, `EXPOSE`

docker user deffrent networking drivers to manage every cases by the real needness



